{"tid":574830,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"人生苦短，有興趣就入group行山/打羽球啦","createTime":"2018-02-27T17:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T17:40:39.000Z","uid":158199,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6d502bc24dd88656e39b913bc8a9904c3fbf3f","tid":574830,"uid":158199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T17:40:39.000Z","msg":"如果你希望可以join一個group係唔需要經常上水睇message，<br />\n間中又可以出來行下山，或打羽球，搵人出來吹下水，唔洗咁自閉，出去見下人，識下朋友，<br />\n除咗返工以外，假期可以出去行下。<br />\n我諗以下依個行山下group會幾適合你。<br />\n暫時平均一個月至少會搞一次行山/戶外活動。<br />\n<br />\n依家個Group打算招多10個鐘意行山，想間中出下來識下朋友的人。Group入面個個都好nice呢!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HAeSJUr6vI4cwvyiYpjJxg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHAeSJUr6vI4cwvyiYpjJxg&d=MP5r6eUwNfSjSFn0NXIBn9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8997346c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HAeSJUr6vI4cwvyiYpjJxg</a><br />\n<br />\n如果鏈結失效，即係個group收夠人啦<br />\n<br />\n貼幾張相引下大家入來先!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/02/28/cDoXG3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2FcDoXG3.jpeg&h=5e8468e3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/02/28/Xe4WK9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2FXe4WK9.jpeg&h=8581e51e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/02/28/Codycb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2FCodycb.jpeg&h=d248e6eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/02/28/MiJvxf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2FMiJvxf.jpeg&h=596cbb85&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/02/28/wHm3XL.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2FwHm3XL.jpeg&h=dd5